snippet.title: Telocation Gemini N64 Homebrew game
snippet.description:
Gameplay and walkthrough for Telocation Gemini on the N64. This is the winning entry for the 2020 64brew game jam. To find out more and download the ROM, visit N64Squid:
https://n64squid.com/telocation-gemini/(opens in a new tab)

00:00 - Menu and opening cutscene
01:00 - Jump To It!
01:35 - Doors and Switches
02:06 - Big Robot Buddy
02:52 - Robot Springboard
04:00 - Big Switch
05:02 - Radioactive
05:51 - Connected Colors
07:02 - Switch Tag Team
08:28 - Inverted Doors
09:47 - Moving Platforms
10:57 - Spiral
12:48 - Loop Around
14:15 - River Crossing
16:22 - Canyon
17:34 - Blocked Track
18:43 - Raised Platform
19:29 - Moving Platforms
20:50 - Switch Maze
22:31 - Robot Raiser
24:20 - Time To Leave
26:55 - End cutscene + credits
27:30 - Multiplayer footage

The video isn't a speedrun and is just a 2nd playthrough, so I fast-forward through the parts that are just wandering around. The video does show where to get all the gems.
